      },
      "rationale": "SST k-ω and realizable k-ε compared against PIV velocity measurements in pump volute; SST k-ω showed 8 % lower mean velocity error and selected. Giersiepen-Wurzinger correlation applicability range (shear stress 0–450 Pa, exposure time 0.001–10 s) verified against operating envelope. Model form uncertainty estimated at ± 12 % NIH. Achieved level 4 meets required level 4."
